branchCategory.name: C(D)UKW, Free Mount Cylinder, Non-rotating, Double Rod
branchCategory.description: <p>The series CUKW double non-rotating rod, double acting free mount cylinder saves space and allows direct and precise mounting. It is available in 6mm to 32mm bore sizes with stroke lengths up to 50mm. Options include auto-switch capabilities, free mount choices, recessed switch mounting grooves and rubber bumpers standard.</p>
